latestPosts.caption:
Three years ago, you stole our hearts, Samaira!

Today, we celebrate the joy, curiosity, and sparkles you bring to our lives. Your infectious laughter is the best medicine, making even the toughest days brighter. Your tiny hands hold ours, and your big, bright smile lights up our world.

You've changed our lives in ways we never thought possible. Mornings are more beautiful because we get to wake up to your sweet smile. Evenings are happening because we get to spend quality time with you. And sleeping next to you is the best thing - it's like having a piece of heaven right here on earth.

Your cuddles are rejuvenating, melting our hearts and soothing our souls. The way you say 'Mummma, you're my best friend' is the most precious thing we've ever heard. You make us feel seen, heard, and loved in ways we never thought possible. 

Happy birthday, baby girl! Papa and mumma love you more than words can say.

#SamairaTurns3 #BirthdayWishes #ProudParents #LoveOfMyLife #GratefulHearts
